-plan-netanyahu-shows-that-international-pressure-is-bearing-fruit/0000018d-d5de-d0da-a3af-fdfe4a590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列推出 2024 年国家资助的医疗保健“篮子”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-rolls-out-state-funded-health-care-basket-for-2024/0000018d-d581-d5f7-a3ff-d7f5b7420000</link><description>增加 6.5 亿谢克尔（1.79 亿美元）的预算将资助新服务和技术，包括生长障碍和严重哮喘的治疗以及扩大侵入性产前筛查测试的资格</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 11:25:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-rolls-out-state-funded-health-care-basket-for-2024/0000018d-d581-d5f7-a3ff-d7f5b7420000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙、白宫和耶路撒冷法庭之间的十字路口，内塔尼亚胡保留了所有选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/between-gaza-the-white-house-and-a-jerusalem-court-netanyahu-is-leaving-all-options-open/0000018d-d509-d74b-addf-d77bf4060000</link><description>埃胡德·巴拉克（Ehud Barak）与国防机构人士一起恳求甘茨和艾森科特不要辞去政府职务；梅龙灾难委员会的调查结果预计将很快公布，这看起来像是总理刑事审判后等待着他的事情的预告片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/between-gaza-the-white-house-and-a-jerusalem-court-netanyahu-is-leaving-all-options-open/0000018d-d509-d74b-addf-d77bf4060000</guid></item><item><title>艾森科特支持内塔尼亚胡的灾难性联盟，助长了以色列极右翼势力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/eisenkot-enables-israels-far-right-firebugs-by-propping-up-netanyahus-coalition/0000018d-d297-df79-a5cd-f2bf819b0000</link><description>民族团结党在紧急政府中的存在正在帮助以色列最大限度地实现其战时目标的幻想已经演变成损害控制 ■ 斯莫特里奇、本格维尔及其同类的“犹太复国主义”是法西斯主义，它将国家置于个人之上</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/eisenkot-enables-israels-far-right-firebugs-by-propping-up-netanyahus-coalition/0000018d-d297-df79-a5cd-f2bf819b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的三个选择：人质交易、拉法攻势或更多空